value.PublicRemarks: Curb appeal galore on the outside and updates galore on the inside!!!  From the frosted front door to the oversized modern 2+ car garage, the details of this home will continue to wow you!  Major updates include newer vinyl windows, new furnace, newer water heater, 30 year architectural shingles, brand new carpet in the lower level and a brand new washer and dryer. The kitchen has been expanded and updated with a center island that features a breakfast bar & a dishwasher. Updated bathroom with a vented glass block window, newer soffits, fascia, exterior window wraps & leaf guard gutters, R50+ insulation in the attic.  Main floor features tall ceilings, a formal dining room with passthrough opening to the kitchen, and extra wide stairs to the lower level.  Freshly painted inside and out, thoughtful landscaping, spacious deck and a concrete driveway complete this perfect move-in ready home with CENTRAL AIR.

value.PublicRemarks:
Stunning Craftsman with an incredible upper-level owner’s suite!! You’re going to love this corner lot 1923 built home that has clearly been well maintained over its 100 years of life!  You will be awestruck by the perfect woodwork throughout. There are tall baseboards, crown molding, window trim, an amazing built-in buffet, & matching built in bookcases in the pristine room divider.  The kitchen has an original wall of cabinets and countertop.  The kitchen also has hardwood floors, a farm style sink & a dishwasher for modern conveniences!  The decorative radiator covers are still in the home; however, the boiler was replaced with a high efficiency furnace & now has CENTRAL AIR conditioning!  There are two bedrooms on the main level & a full bathroom.  The upstairs suite will blow you away – windows on all 4 walls, full bath, wide plank floors & plenty of headroom!  The backyard is fenced in, and the lot has been nicely landscaped. 
 Request a tour now!

value.PublicRemarks:
First time offering! Custom built 2 bedroom home featuring high vaulted ceilings, main floor living on
beautiful Bass Lake. Outstanding and peaceful 3+ acre lot that is level to lake with 640ft of frontage. Property is beautifully landscaped with lovely perennial gardens, wide open panoramic views of the lake and even has a private setting. Plenty of storage with two metal buildings, one heated. The homes open floor plan is perfect for entertaining! Enjoy the gas fireplace in the living room with its custom cultured stone and comfortable seating.
Primary bedroom is spacious and includes a 3/4 bath with an indoor sauna and walk in closet! If you are looking for one level living, look no further! This slab on grade home has in floor heat, off peak water heater, dual fuel, main floor laundry. Enjoy peaceful mornings or evenings on the lake side patio watching the loons and other wild life, or get out on the lake and catch dinner for a fish fry, this property will not disappoint!

Living room adjoins formal dining room, creating a fabulous entertainment room. Updated gourmet kitchen offers maple cabinets, under cabinet lights; cabinets and cupboards galore. Off the informal dining area are 2 different sliders that bring you to your own private paradise patios. Down the hall, you will find 3 nice sized bedrooms. Master suite offers your own private bath with double sinks, tiled walk-in shower and 2 closets. Lower level is ready for entertaining with expanded wet bar, built-in cabinetry, wine fridge, fireplace and lots of space. Oversized bedroom with Cali walk-in closet. Updated bath. Lower level could be a mother in-law apt.
